You could sort the bullets and the enemies (prefer Shell sort or Heapsort) before comparing them. That will help you trivially reject more hitboxes at once.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Tue Sep 13, 2005 11:47 am</p><hr />
